result.name: Tsui Wah Restaurant

reviews.text: A bit dim light here.  Service and food were alright.  Another same style restaurant was located along the street.
Good food and not too expensive. Milk tea is excellent.
Very good food and friendly staff!

This is a chain of restaurants mushrooming across the city which gets you quick service anytime of the day at very affordable prices. You get all sorts of food in here right from steaks to Chinese food. It's worth going if you are particular on your pocket spends.
If your British and struggling with local food this place is a safe bet. A little pricey though.

reviews.text: 最好休息2AM🙌🙌🙌🙌🙌🙆🙆
環境清净，态度和慈愛的感覺。餐桌上干淨。品味繁多，真正值得去感受著她和藹可親。
呢度嘅地點比較方便，食物水準都可以，但衛生就一般，而且有部份嘅waitress態度比較差，唔理事。有人投訴地下有小強，該waitress可以當聽唔到，睇唔到就走Q咗，好差。但見到啲男食客就笑哂口，姣性又發哂作。當然唔係個個waitress都係如上述個位，有些很有禮貌。
